=== Saved Equivalence Conjectures ===
- ((connected) ∧ (bipartite) ∧ (chordal)) ≡ ((connected) ∧ (tree))
- ((connected) ∧ (bipartite) ∧ (cograph)) ≡ ((connected) ∧ (cograph) ∧ (triangle_free))

=== Joint Generalizations (Slope/Intercept/Reciprocals) ===
- ((connected) ∧ (bipartite)) ⇒ independence_number ≤ order + chromatic_number/clique_number
- ((connected) ∧ (chordal)) ⇒ independence_number ≤ order + chromatic_number/clique_number
- ((connected) ∧ (bipartite)) ⇒ independence_number ≤ order + clique_number/chromatic_number
- ((connected) ∧ (chordal)) ⇒ independence_number ≤ order + clique_number/chromatic_number
- ((connected) ∧ (bipartite)) ⇒ independence_number ≤ order + matching_number/vertex_cover_number
- ((connected) ∧ (bipartite)) ⇒ independence_number ≤ order + vertex_cover_number/matching_number
- ((connected) ∧ (bipartite)) ⇒ independence_number ≤ order + (chromatic_number - 1)/chromatic_number
- ((connected) ∧ (bipartite)) ⇒ independence_number ≤ order + chromatic_number/(chromatic_number + 1)
- ((connected) ∧ (bipartite)) ⇒ independence_number ≤ order + (chromatic_number + 1)/chromatic_number
- ((connected) ∧ (bipartite)) ⇒ independence_number ≤ order + chromatic_number/(chromatic_number - 1)
- ((connected) ∧ (bipartite)) ⇒ independence_number ≤ order + (chromatic_number - 1)/clique_number
- ((connected) ∧ (bipartite)) ⇒ independence_number ≤ order + chromatic_number/(clique_number + 1)
